{"tid":2330620,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美副總統彭斯：會和川普繼續戰鬥  直到剔除所有非法票","createTime":"2020-12-18T07:22:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-18T07:52:49.000Z","uid":184679,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"eeee66421a0deac7bea9440c8b928f8167626faf","tid":2330620,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T07:22:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ntdtv.com/assets/uploads/2020/12/11-33-600x338.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ntdtv.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F12%2F11-33-600x338.jpg&h=6a877c0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國副總統彭斯（Mike Pence）。（Ethan Miller/Getty Images）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國副總統彭斯12月17日前往喬治亞州，為兩名共和黨參議員連任助選。他在集會上說，將和川普（特朗普）總統繼續戰鬥，直到剔除所有非法選票。<br />\n<br />\n據大紀元報導，彭斯在喬治亞州哥倫布（Columbus）舉行的一次集會上表示，「對於你們每個人，我都會向你保證，隨著我們的選舉挑戰在全美各地法院推進，我們將繼續戰鬥，直到計算出每一合法票為止。」<br />\n<br />\n他還表示，將永遠不會停止為使美國再次偉大而奮鬥。<br />\n<br />\n彭斯此行旨在激勵川普支持者，和其他共和黨人，投票給共和黨參議員戴維‧珀杜（David Perdue）和凱利‧洛夫勒（Kelly Loeffler），以便共和黨能贏得參議院多數席位。<br />\n<br />\n彭斯說，「我知道我們都對上次選舉（11月3日總統選舉）表示懷疑」，但他承諾「我們將確保我們的投票觀察員，確保我們的投票箱安全，並且你可以確信自己的缺席選票將被計算在內。」<br />\n<br />\n他說：「我們將贏得喬治亞州，我們將拯救美國。」<br />\n<br />\n12月5日，川普前往喬治亞州參加大規模集會並發表演講，川普說：「我們繼續戰鬥。」<br />\n<br />\n他說，他們（民主黨）操縱總統選舉，但他仍然要贏得大選。川普也強調，民主黨還想操縱參議員競選。<br />\n<br />\n川普總統拒絕承認拜登當選，川普團隊指控在關鍵搖擺州存在大規模選民欺詐。川普上週日在推特上說，本次總統大選是「美國歷史上最腐敗的選舉！」<br />\n<br />\n據報導，明年1月6日，美國國會將召開聯席會議認證各州遞交的選舉人團投票結果，屆時參眾兩院全體大會將確認當選總統。<br />\n<br />\n根據憲法第12修正案規定，彭斯要在兩院出席的情況下公開所有選舉人證書並點算票數。但是按國會規定，只要同時有一名參議員和一名眾議員反對，就可挑戰選舉人票取向決定，反對拜登勝選結果。之後將由參議院及眾議院分別投選副總統及總統人選。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/2020/12/18/a103012737.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ntdtv.com%2Fb5%2F2020%2F12%2F18%2Fa103012737.html&d=PGKZrCzpIeFm7bz4D1EKrWqRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=530e6e56\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/2020/12/18/a103012737.html</a>"},{"pid":"d5a0d27003ab35c62c82d31d8ebbba422bd1d927","tid":2330620,"uid":63909,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T07:23:34.000Z","msg":"人正氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d85a2a1ba8ee568bcb75ebc72da97c6e66c250d8","tid":2330620,"uid":345989,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T07:28:08.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">MAGA<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"816c6cff56d3d222b30a1d0cc1086a2a0665434e","tid":2330620,"uid":54622,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T07:31:42.000Z","msg":"MAGA<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae6017dd53025ea1f1f93a82dc89ff710fe9b66f","tid":2330620,"uid":51546,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T07:36:44.000Z","msg":"我覺得拜登會贏<br />\n too big to fail"},{"pid":"28bc4ebe94a07a95dd9440fc46aeaea61861aaeb","tid":2330620,"uid":62749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T07:37:17.000Z","msg":"最緊要團結"},{"pid":"4f0bf1519f9f28f36e28ea278fd47145a3be86a0","tid":2330620,"uid":52369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T07:38:14.000Z","msg":"GOP贏唔贏到都成問題 米奇豬隊友"},{"pid":"ac0099dae34296c9bc9ede0c4d73ebf9fb77be2c","tid":2330620,"uid":156121,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T07:39:03.000Z","msg":"一月六日GA參議院贏番就可以玩權變"},{"pid":"e2a77f4801bbd600759521f8cc592ac8ff773e94","tid":2330620,"uid":158499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T07:39:19.000Z","msg":"Nice move<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68dbe3344b38bd496ed72bf25bfe8354d50413c0","tid":2330620,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T07:40:16.000Z","msg":"搞左咁多個月重係想用點票方法贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7641980af900f77edeff7ede79cc37f25cf7e76","tid":2330620,"uid":256142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T07:50:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b49168b55abd335ba698420b7b59bbf60606fe1","tid":2330620,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T07:52:49.000Z","msg":"In彭斯 we7 阿侵收皮啦"}]}